{"tid":1335324,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[數學題] 添馬公園1.7萬平方米10萬人, 維園4萬平方米幾多人?","createTime":"2019-07-20T12:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T14:36:22.000Z","uid":49220,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e33d26c17ef035ea98d076be616b35a9f8c33586","tid":1335324,"uid":49220,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:54:36.000Z","msg":"添馬公園面積為17000米,<br />\n警方數據高峰期10.2萬人, 每平方米6人<br />\n大會數據最多有31.6萬人, 每平方米18.6人<br />\n(提示, 港鐵表示, 列車最滿可以容納每平方米4人)<br />\n<br />\n而維園六個足球場, 面積為3380平方米 x 6 =20280平方米<br />\n維園草地面積為9800平方米<br />\n2019年六四30週年晚會, 6個足球場及中央草地&quot;同樣全滿&quot;, 面積為20280+9800=40080平方米,<br />\n那麼請問六四30週年晚會人數為多少?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n答案: 警方則指2019年六四集會高峰人數有 3.7 萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n為孩子及長輩增長數學知識, 請廣傳！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c9ecb9228efb96d53e2a7b2b0b2a573b0ff49f1","tid":1335324,"uid":20890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:58:05.000Z","msg":"大會31萬人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />吹到傻撚左"},{"pid":"21f7aef9b709067d92bc977984c00f89965e79db","tid":1335324,"uid":267600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T12:59:25.000Z","msg":"吹大不用腦！"},{"pid":"d8f43eb2bac61080feb7bdd964e79270a695a6c5","tid":1335324,"uid":49220,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:06:39.000Z","msg":"地鐵逼到沙甸魚咁, 都係每平方米4人,<br />\n撐警集會每平方米18.6人, 後先有冇發生人踩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5dcbbe7e7b7c1700e002a43b634ffee98ac95ca2","tid":1335324,"uid":183515,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-20T13:10:59.000Z","msg":"毅進制唔屬於數學範疇，屬於公民教育，睇下計果個有幾無恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"335f1bd89445b7c5a04ad9d6243c1ca8c8afbfac","tid":1335324,"uid":81652,"like":0,"dis